#. <a class="nya" id="nya10"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "mn78:10.1"
msgid "Katame ca, thapati, akusalā sīlā?"
msgstr "And what, master builder, are unskillful behaviors?"

msgctxt "mn78:10.2"
msgid "Akusalaṃ kāyakammaṃ, akusalaṃ vacīkammaṃ, pāpako ājīvo—"
msgstr "Unskillful deeds by way of body and speech, and bad livelihood."

msgctxt "mn78:10.3"
msgid "ime vuccanti, thapati, akusalā sīlā."
msgstr "These are called unskillful behaviors."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "mn78:10.4"
msgid "Ime ca, thapati, akusalā sīlā kiṃsamuṭṭhānā?"
msgstr "And where do these unskillful behaviors stem from?"

msgctxt "mn78:10.5"
msgid "Samuṭṭhānampi nesaṃ vuttaṃ."
msgstr "Where they stem from has been stated."

msgctxt "mn78:10.6"
msgid "‘Cittasamuṭṭhānā’tissa vacanīyaṃ."
msgstr "You should say that they stem from the mind."

msgctxt "mn78:10.7"
msgid "Katamaṃ cittaṃ?"
msgstr "What mind?"

msgctxt "mn78:10.8"
msgid "Cittampi hi bahuṃ anekavidhaṃ nānappakārakaṃ."
msgstr "The mind takes many and diverse forms."

msgctxt "mn78:10.9"
msgid "Yaṃ cittaṃ sarāgaṃ sadosaṃ samohaṃ, itosamuṭṭhānā akusalā sīlā."
msgstr ""
"But unskillful behaviors stem from a mind that has greed, hate, and delusion."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc14"></a>
msgctxt "mn78:10.10"
msgid "Ime ca, thapati, akusalā sīlā kuhiṃ aparisesā nirujjhanti?"
msgstr ""
"And where do these unskillful behaviors cease without anything left over?"

msgctxt "mn78:10.11"
msgid "Nirodhopi nesaṃ vutto."
msgstr "Their cessation has also been stated."

msgctxt "mn78:10.12"
msgid ""
"Idha, thapati, bhikkhu kāyaduccaritaṃ pahāya kāyasucaritaṃ bhāveti, "
"vacīduccaritaṃ pahāya vacīsucaritaṃ bhāveti, manoduccaritaṃ pahāya "
"manosucaritaṃ bhāveti, micchājīvaṃ pahāya sammājīvena jīvitaṃ kappeti—"
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant gives up bad conduct by way of body, speech, and mind, "
"and develops good conduct by way of body, speech, and mind; they give up "
"wrong livelihood and earn a living by right livelihood."

msgctxt "mn78:10.13"
msgid "etthete akusalā sīlā aparisesā nirujjhanti."
msgstr ""
"This is where these unskillful behaviors cease without anything left over."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi2.27"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc15"></a>
msgctxt "mn78:10.14"
msgid "Kathaṃ paṭipanno, thapati, akusalānaṃ sīlānaṃ nirodhāya paṭipanno hoti?"
msgstr ""
"And how is someone practicing for the cessation of unskillful behaviors?"

msgctxt "mn78:10.15"
msgid ""
"Idha, thapati, bhikkhu anuppannānaṃ pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ "
"anuppādāya chandaṃ janeti vāyamati vīriyaṃ ārabhati cittaṃ paggaṇhāti "
"padahati;"
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant generates enthusiasm, tries, makes an effort, exerts "
"the mind, and strives so that bad, unskillful qualities don’t arise."

msgctxt "mn78:10.16"
msgid ""
"uppannānaṃ pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya chandaṃ janeti vāyamati "
"vīriyaṃ ārabhati cittaṃ paggaṇhāti padahati;"
msgstr ""
"They generate enthusiasm, try, make an effort, exert the mind, and strive so "
"that bad, unskillful qualities that have arisen are given up."

msgctxt "mn78:10.17"
msgid ""
"anuppannānaṃ kusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ uppādāya chandaṃ janeti vāyamati vīriyaṃ "
"ārabhati cittaṃ paggaṇhāti padahati;"
msgstr ""
"They generate enthusiasm, try, make an effort, exert the mind, and strive so "
"that skillful qualities arise."

msgctxt "mn78:10.18"
msgid ""
"uppannānaṃ kusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ ṭhitiyā asammosāya bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya "
"bhāvanāya pāripūriyā chandaṃ janeti vāyamati vīriyaṃ ārabhati cittaṃ "
"paggaṇhāti padahati."
msgstr ""
"They generate enthusiasm, try, make an effort, exert the mind, and strive so "
"that skillful qualities that have arisen remain, are not lost, but increase, "
"mature, and are completed by development."

msgctxt "mn78:10.19"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ paṭipanno kho, thapati, akusalānaṃ sīlānaṃ nirodhāya paṭipanno hoti."
msgstr ""
"Someone practicing like this is practicing for the cessation of unskillful "
"behaviors."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya11"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc16"></a>
msgctxt "mn78:11.1"
msgid "Katame ca, thapati, kusalā sīlā?"
msgstr "And what are skillful behaviors?"

msgctxt "mn78:11.2"
msgid ""
"Kusalaṃ kāyakammaṃ, kusalaṃ vacīkammaṃ, ājīvaparisuddhampi kho ahaṃ, "
"thapati, sīlasmiṃ vadāmi."
msgstr ""
"Skillful deeds by way of body and speech, and purified livelihood are "
"included in behavior, I say."

msgctxt "mn78:11.3"
msgid "Ime vuccanti, thapati, kusalā sīlā."
msgstr "These are called skillful behaviors."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc17"></a>
msgctxt "mn78:11.4"
msgid "Ime ca, thapati, kusalā sīlā kiṃsamuṭṭhānā?"
msgstr "And where do these skillful behaviors stem from?"

msgctxt "mn78:11.5"
msgid "Samuṭṭhānampi nesaṃ vuttaṃ."
msgstr "Where they stem from has been stated."

msgctxt "mn78:11.6"
msgid "‘Cittasamuṭṭhānā’tissa vacanīyaṃ."
msgstr "You should say that they stem from the mind."

msgctxt "mn78:11.7"
msgid "Katamaṃ cittaṃ?"
msgstr "What mind?"

msgctxt "mn78:11.8"
msgid "Cittampi hi bahuṃ anekavidhaṃ nānappakārakaṃ."
msgstr "The mind takes many and diverse forms."

msgctxt "mn78:11.9"
msgid "Yaṃ cittaṃ vītarāgaṃ vītadosaṃ vītamohaṃ, itosamuṭṭhānā kusalā sīlā."
msgstr ""
"But skillful behaviors stem from a mind that is free from greed, hate, and "
"delusion."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc18"></a>
msgctxt "mn78:11.10"
msgid "Ime ca, thapati, kusalā sīlā kuhiṃ aparisesā nirujjhanti?"
msgstr "And where do these skillful behaviors cease without anything left over?"

msgctxt "mn78:11.11"
msgid "Nirodhopi nesaṃ vutto."
msgstr "Their cessation has also been stated."

# Following BB, taking the suffix -maya in the same sense as atammaya.
msgctxt "mn78:11.12"
msgid "Idha, thapati, bhikkhu sīlavā hoti no ca sīlamayo, "
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant behaves ethically, but they don’t identify with their "
"ethical behavior. "

msgctxt "mn78:11.13"
msgid ""
"tañca cetovimuttiṃ paññāvimuttiṃ yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti; yatthassa te kusalā "
"sīlā aparisesā nirujjhanti."
msgstr ""
"And they truly understand the freedom of heart and freedom by wisdom where "
"these skillful behaviors cease without anything left over."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc19"></a>
msgctxt "mn78:11.14"
msgid ""
"Kathaṃ paṭipanno ca, thapati, kusalānaṃ sīlānaṃ nirodhāya paṭipanno hoti?"
msgstr "And how is someone practicing for the cessation of skillful behaviors?"

