#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya12"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc20"></a>
msgctxt "mn78:12.1"
msgid "Katame ca, thapati, akusalā saṅkappā?"
msgstr "And what are unskillful thoughts?"

