msgstr "You should say that they stem from perception."

msgctxt "mn78:12.7"
msgid "Katamā saññā?"
msgstr "What perception?"

msgctxt "mn78:12.8"
msgid "Saññāpi hi bahū anekavidhā nānappakārakā."
msgstr "Perception takes many and diverse forms."

msgctxt "mn78:12.9"
msgid "Kāmasaññā, byāpādasaññā, vihiṃsāsaññā—"
msgstr "Perceptions of sensuality, malice, and cruelty—"

msgctxt "mn78:12.10"
msgid "itosamuṭṭhānā akusalā saṅkappā."
msgstr "unskillful thoughts stem from this."

#. </p><p>
