msgid "Ime ca, thapati, akusalā saṅkappā kuhiṃ aparisesā nirujjhanti?"
msgstr ""
"And where do these unskillful thoughts cease without anything left over?"

msgctxt "mn78:12.12"
msgid "Nirodhopi nesaṃ vutto."
msgstr "Their cessation has also been stated."

msgctxt "mn78:12.13"
msgid ""
"Idha, thapati, bhikkhu vivicceva kāmehi … pe … paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja "
"viharati;"
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant, quite secluded from sensual pleasures, secluded from "
"unskillful qualities, enters and remains in the first absorption, which has "
"the rapture and bliss born of seclusion, while placing the mind and keeping "
"it connected."

msgctxt "mn78:12.14"
msgid "etthete akusalā saṅkappā aparisesā nirujjhanti."
msgstr ""
"This is where these unskillful thoughts cease without anything left over."

#. </p><p>
