#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya14"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi2.29"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc28"></a>
msgctxt "mn78:14.1"
msgid ""
"Katamehi cāhaṃ, thapati, dasahi dhammehi samannāgataṃ purisapuggalaṃ "
"paññapemi sampannakusalaṃ paramakusalaṃ uttamapattipattaṃ samaṇaṃ ayojjhaṃ?"
msgstr ""
"Master builder, when an individual has what ten qualities do I describe them "
"as an invincible ascetic—accomplished in the skillful, excelling in the "
"skillful, attained to the highest attainment?"

msgctxt "mn78:14.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, thapati, bhikkhu asekhāya sammādiṭṭhiyā samannāgato hoti, asekhena "
"sammāsaṅkappena samannāgato hoti, asekhāya sammāvācāya samannāgato hoti, "
"asekhena sammākammantena samannāgato hoti, asekhena sammāājīvena samannāgato "
"hoti, asekhena sammāvāyāmena samannāgato hoti, asekhāya sammāsatiyā "
"samannāgato hoti, asekhena sammāsamādhinā samannāgato hoti, asekhena "
"sammāñāṇena samannāgato hoti, asekhāya sammāvimuttiyā samannāgato hoti—"
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant has an adept’s right view, right thought, right "
"speech, right action, right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, "
"right immersion, right knowledge, and right freedom."

msgctxt "mn78:14.3"
msgid ""
"imehi kho ahaṃ, thapati, dasahi dhammehi samannāgataṃ purisapuggalaṃ "
"paññapemi sampannakusalaṃ paramakusalaṃ uttamapattipattaṃ samaṇaṃ "
"ayojjhan”ti."
msgstr ""
"When an individual has these ten qualities, I describe them as an invincible "
"ascetic—accomplished in the skillful, excelling in the skillful, attained to "
"the highest attainment.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc29"></a>
msgctxt "mn78:14.4"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā."
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said."

msgctxt "mn78:14.5"
msgid "Attamano pañcakaṅgo thapati bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinandīti."
msgstr ""
"Satisfied, Pañcakaṅga the master builder was happy with what the Buddha said."

#. </p><p class="endsection">
